2003年10月，{{le|Team Soho|Team Soho}}负责《{{le|大逃亡 (游戏)|The Getaway (video game)|大逃亡}}》的总监布伦丹·麦克纳马拉离开这家伦敦的公司，回到母国澳大利亚自立工作室[[Team_Bondi|Team Bondi]]。这家最初只有6个人的工作室刚成立不久，便宣布他们的首个项目面向“索尼的次世代平台”<ref name="First"/>。2004年，麦克纳马拉表示该计划完全由[[索尼互动娱乐|索尼互动娱乐]]提供支持<ref name="First">{{cite web |title=Team Bondi – The First Interview |url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/i_teambondi |first=Tom |last=Bramwell |website=Eurogamer |date=2004-02-20 |access-date=2007-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090324160450/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/i_teambondi |archive-date=2009-03-24 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2005年，游戏名称“黑色洛城”和[[PlayStation_3|PlayStation 3]]独占发行的消息公布。Team Bondi形容游戏属于“刑侦惊悚类”<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/team-bondi-announces-ps3-game/1100-6129334/ |title=Team Bondi announces PS3 game |last=Surette |first=Tim |work=GameSpot |publisher=CBS Interactive |date=2005-07-18 |access-date=2014-07-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140822092127/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/team-bondi-announces-ps3-game/1100-6129334/ |archive-date=2014-08-22 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2006年9月，消息指[[Rockstar_Games|Rockstar Games]]将处理游戏的发布工作，不过Rockstar仅称游戏是“次世代犯罪惊悚游戏”，未指明平台<ref>{{cite web |last=Surette |first=Tim |url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/rockstar-gets-la-noire/1100-6158595/ |title=Rockstar gets L.A. Noire |work=GameSpot |publisher=CBS Interactive |date=2011-05-20 |access-date=2012-05-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140822092213/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/rockstar-gets-la-noire/1100-6158595/ |archive-date=2014-08-22 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2007年6月，Rockstar母公司[[Take-Two_Interactive|Take-Two Interactive]]将游戏列入“2008年财年”作品名录，重新确认作品在PlayStation 3平台发行，日期“有待公布”<ref name="take2games2007">{{cite press release|title=Second Quarter Fiscal 2007 Financial Results |url=http://ir.take2games.com/phoenix.zhtml?c=86428&p=irol-newsArticle&ID=1013916 |publisher=Take-Two Interactive |date=2007-06-11 |access-date=2007-06-15 }}</ref>。Take-Two的发言人后来暗示游戏可能也在[[Xbox_360|Xbox 360]]发行<ref name="NGS">{{cite web|title=Rockstar confirms: episodic GTA content 360-only L.A. Noire developed for Next-Gen Systems|url=http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/rockstar-confirms-episodic-gta-content-360-only |first=Mark |last=Androvich |publisher=GamesIndustry.biz |date=2007-06-16 |access-date=2007-04-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080409182125/http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/rockstar-confirms-episodic-gta-content-360-only |archive-date=2008-04-09 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。后来在2007年9月，Take-Two宣布发售窗口延期至2009年财年<ref>{{cite web |title=BioShock A Long Term Franchise, LA Noire, Beaterator Slip To Fiscal 2009 |url=http://www.gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=15447 |first=Brandon |last=Boyer |work=Gamasutra |publisher=UBM plc |date=2007-09-10 |access-date=2007-09-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070810001016/http://www.gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=15447 |archive-date=2007-08-10 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2010年3月的《[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]]》确认游戏将于2010年9月在PlayStation 3和Xbox 360发行<ref name="BarReset">{{cite web |url=http://www.gameinformer.com/games/la_noire/b/xbox360/archive/2010/11/11/l-a-noire-preview.aspx |title=Rockstar Resets The Bar With Its Upcoming Crime Thriller - L.A. Noire |last=Helgeson |first=Matt |work=Game Informer |publisher=GameStop |date=2010-11-11 |access-date=2014-06-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101112192142/http://gameinformer.com/games/la_noire/b/xbox360/archive/2010/11/11/l-a-noire-preview.aspx |archive-date=2010-11-12 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=March Cover Revealed |url=http://gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2010/02/04/march-cover-revealed.aspx |last=Cork |first=Jeff |work=Game Informer |publisher=GameStop |date=2010-02-04 |access-date=2010-02-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100206213253/http://gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2010/02/04/march-cover-revealed.aspx |archive-date=2010-02-06 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，然而游戏并未如期面世，Take-Two将日期推迟到2011年上半年<ref name="eurogamer">{{cite web |last=Yin-Poole |first=Wesley |url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2010-11-11-l-a-noire-out-spring-2011 |title=L.A. Noire out spring 2011|website=Eurogamer |date=2010-11-11 |access-date=2010-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101113195506/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2010-11-11-l-a-noire-out-spring-2011 |archive-date=2010-11-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/11651/la-noire-first-trailer-coming-thursday-november-11th.html |title=L.A. Noire First Trailer Coming - Thursday November 11th |publisher=Rockstar Games |date=2010-11-08 |access-date=2010-11-10 |archive-date=2021-02-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227222730/https://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/11651/la-noire-first-trailer-coming-thursday-november-11th.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，认为延期利于游戏取得成功<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/red-dead-redeems-take-two-earnings-ships-69m/1100-6274962/ |title=Red Dead redeems Take-Two earnings, ships 6.9M |first=Brendan |last=Sinclair |work=GameSpot |publisher=CBS Interactive |date=2010-09-02 |access-date=2012-05-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140822091820/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/red-dead-redeems-take-two-earnings-ships-69m/1100-6274962/ |archive-date=2014-08-22 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。档期后来精确到2011年3月<ref>{{cite web|url=http://blog.us.playstation.com/2011/01/17/l-a-noire-muscles-its-way-onto-the-cover-of-playstation-the-official-magazine/ |title=L.A. Noire Muscles Its Way Onto the Cover of PlayStation: The Official Magazine |last=Steinman |first=Gary |publisher=PlayStation Blog |date=2011-01-17 |access-date=2011-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110120055613/http://blog.us.playstation.com/2011/01/17/l-a-noire-muscles-its-way-onto-the-cover-of-playstation-the-official-magazine/ |archive-date=2011-01-20 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但最终延期至5月17日发行<ref name="GameSpot">{{cite web |url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/la-noire-emerging-from-shadows-may-17/1100-6286823/ |title=L.A. Noire emerging from shadows May 17 |last=Makuch |first=Eddie |work=GameSpot |publisher=CBS Interactive |date=2011-01-22 |access-date=2010-01-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140822092028/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/la-noire-emerging-from-shadows-may-17/1100-6286823/ |archive-date=2014-08-22 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 推广 ===
大量预告片及媒体演示会对游戏进行推广。《[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]]》2010年2月号刊登了《黑色洛城》的封面故事<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/3151/la-noire-cover-story-in-this-months-game-informer.html |title=L.A. Noire Cover Story in this Month's Game Informer |publisher=Rockstar Games |date=2010-02-08 |access-date=2014-06-21 |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303234724/http://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/3151/la-noire-cover-story-in-this-months-game-informer.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2010年11月12日，首支预告片发行，展示游戏多个场景，由赫歇尔·比格斯的扮演者基斯·萨拉巴吉卡旁白<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/11751/watch-the-la-noire-first-trailer.html |title=Watch the L.A. Noire First Trailer |publisher=Rockstar Games |date=2010-11-12 |access-date=2014-06-21 |archive-date=2020-11-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201123164733/https://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/11751/watch-the-la-noire-first-trailer.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2010年12月16日，首支记录发行开发过程幕后视频《表演背后的技术》（"The Technology Behind Performance"）发布，展示游戏采用的MotionScan技术，以及对演出人员及开发团队的采访<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/12361/watch-the-new-la-noire-video-the-technology-behind-performance.html |title=Watch the New L.A. Noire Video "The Technology Behind Performance" |publisher=Rockstar Games |date=2010-12-16 |access-date=2014-06-21 |archive-date=2014-07-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140728170422/http://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/12361/watch-the-new-la-noire-video-the-technology-behind-performance.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。第二支预告片于2011年1月24日发行，着重介绍游戏的凶杀科案件<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/13121/watch-the-allnew-la-noire-official-trailer-2.html |title=Watch the All-New L.A. Noire Official Trailer #2 |publisher=Rockstar Games |date=2011-01-24 |access-date=2014-06-21 |archive-date=2020-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201019220142/https://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/13121/watch-the-allnew-la-noire-official-trailer-2.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。第三支预告片《方向》（"Orientation"）发布，演示游戏的审讯和调查机制，展示战斗元素<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/13551/watch-the-first-la-noire-gameplay-series-video-orientation.html |title=Watch the First L.A. Noire Gameplay Series Video: "Orientation" |publisher=Rockstar Games |date=2011-02-09 |access-date=2014-06-21 |archive-date=2021-03-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210302192625/https://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/13551/watch-the-first-la-noire-gameplay-series-video-orientation.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。游戏封面于2011年2月23日揭开面纱<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/13931/la-noire-official-cover-art-revealed-plus-look-for-details-on-ex.html |title=L.A. Noire Official Cover Art Revealed Plus Look for Details on Exclusive Pre-Order Bonus Content Tomorrow |publisher=Rockstar Games |date=2011-02-23 |access-date=2014-06-21 |archive-date=2020-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111203827/http://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/13931/la-noire-official-cover-art-revealed-plus-look-for-details-on-ex.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，次日预购专享内容公布<ref name="preorder">{{cite web |url=http://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/14011/presenting-preorder-exclusive-unlockable-bonus-content-when-you-.html |title=Presenting Pre-Order Exclusive Unlockable Bonus Content when You Pre-Order L.A. Noire: Cases, Challenges, Suits & More |publisher=Rockstar Games |date=2011-02-24 |access-date=2014-06-21 |archive-date=2014-10-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141009114634/http://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/14011/presenting-preorder-exclusive-unlockable-bonus-content-when-you-.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

预购案件预告片于3月3日<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/14181/watch-the-allnew-la-noire-video-for-the-naked-city-preorder-excl.html |title=Watch the All-New L.A. Noire Video for "The Naked City" Pre-Order Exclusive Vice Desk Case |publisher=Rockstar Games |date=2011-03-03 |access-date=2014-06-21 |archive-date=2014-07-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140728170551/http://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/14181/watch-the-allnew-la-noire-video-for-the-naked-city-preorder-excl.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>和3月31日公布<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/14911/watch-the-new-la-noire-a-slip-of-the-tongue-traffic-desk-preorde.html |title=Watch the New L.A. Noire "A Slip of the Tongue" Traffic Desk Preorder Bonus Case Video |publisher=Rockstar Games |date=2011-03-31 |access-date=2014-06-21 |archive-date=2014-07-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140728171226/http://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/14911/watch-the-new-la-noire-a-slip-of-the-tongue-traffic-desk-preorde.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。3月9日，介绍游戏调查及审讯机制的玩法预告片《调查与审讯》（"Investigation and Interrogation"）公布<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/14301/watch-the-new-la-noire-gameplay-series-video-investigation-and-i.html |title=Watch the New L.A. Noire Gameplay Series Video: "Investigation and Interrogation" |publisher=Rockstar Games |date=2011-03-09 |access-date=2014-06-21 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304053045/http://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/14301/watch-the-new-la-noire-gameplay-series-video-investigation-and-i.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2011年3月的[[PAX游戏展|PAX游戏展]]的展示专场及展位了《黑色洛城》<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/14291/come-check-out-la-noire-at-pax-east-this-weekend.html |title=Come Check Out L.A. Noire at PAX East this Weekend |publisher=Rockstar Games |date=2011-03-09 |access-date=2014-06-21 |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303233614/http://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/14291/come-check-out-la-noire-at-pax-east-this-weekend.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。第三支预告片于2011年4月8日发布，介绍游戏对警局腐败及监察科的描绘<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/15101/watch-the-allnew-la-noire-official-trailer-3.html |title=Watch the All-New L.A. Noire Official Trailer #3 |publisher=Rockstar Games |date=2011-04-08 |access-date=2014-06-21 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112014428/https://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/15101/watch-the-allnew-la-noire-official-trailer-3.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。5月11日，最后一支预告片公布<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/15951/watch-the-la-noire-official-launch-trailer.html |title=Watch the L.A Noire Official Launch Trailer |publisher=Rockstar Games |date=2011-05-11 |access-date=2014-06-21 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112030510/https://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/15951/watch-the-la-noire-official-launch-trailer.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

游戏的营销工作也采用了[[病毒营销|病毒营销]]策略。游戏官方网站于2011年1月27日被重新设计，供玩家预览游戏角色及案件<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/13161/la-noire-official-site-is-now-live.html |title=L.A. Noire Official Site Is Now Live |publisher=Rockstar Games |date=2011-01-27 |access-date=2014-06-20 |archive-date=2017-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171201035444/http://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/13161/la-noire-official-site-is-now-live.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2011年4月25日，游戏入选[[翠贝卡电影节|翠贝卡电影节]]官方片单，是首部参加该影展的电子游戏<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/14861/la-noire-honored-as-first-videogame-to-make-official-selection-o.html |title=L.A. Noire Honored as First Videogame to Make Official Selection of the Tribeca Film Festival |publisher=Rockstar Games |date=2011-03-29 |access-date=2014-06-21 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112030455/https://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/14861/la-noire-honored-as-first-videogame-to-make-official-selection-o.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。Rockstar还举办比赛，胜者有机会前往洛杉矶参加{{le|格劳曼埃及剧院|Grauman's Egyptian Theatre|}}的黑色电影展（Festival of Film Noir），提前一个月前玩到游戏<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/14331/the-los-angeles-noire-weekend-sweepstakes.html |title=The Los Angeles Noire Weekend Sweepstakes |publisher=Rockstar Games |date=2011-03-25 |access-date=2012-02-03 |archive-date=2017-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171201041810/http://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/14331/the-los-angeles-noire-weekend-sweepstakes.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。游戏还亮相2011年4月的一期《{{le|杰夫·基斯利与GameTrailers TV|GameTrailers TV with Geoff Keighley}}》，节目展示了MotionScan技术及对开发团队的专访<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/15281/la-noire-on-latest-episode-of-gttv-on-spike.html |title=L.A. Noire on Latest Episode of GTTV on Spike |publisher=Rockstar Games |date=2011-04-15 |access-date=2014-06-21 |archive-date=2017-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171201040845/http://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/15281/la-noire-on-latest-episode-of-gttv-on-spike.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

为了刺激预购销量，Rockstar联合多家零售商推出预购奖励，包括追加案件《无心快语》（A Slip of the Tongue）和《不夜城》（The Naked City）、支线任务“徽章追逐挑战”（The Badge Pursuit Challenge）、奖励警探西装“The Broderick”和“The Sharpshooter”。Rockstar Games和《黑色洛城》衬衫也是预购奖励<ref name="preorder"/>。除了预购奖励，追加案件《领事的车》（The Consul's Car）也包括在PlayStation 3北美版中，后来在[[PlayStation_Store|PlayStation Store]]开放购买，最终收录于《完整版》（''The Complete Edition''）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://blog.eu.playstation.com/2011/07/27/heads-up-game-store-update-27th-july-2011/ |title='Heads-Up' Game Store Update 27th July 2011 |last=McGrath |first=Ross |publisher=PlayStation Blog |date=2011-07-27 |access-date=2011-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110921140047/http://blog.eu.playstation.com/2011/07/27/heads-up-game-store-update-27th-july-2011/ |archive-date=2011-09-21 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2011年6月6日，Rockstar联合{{le|穆赫兰书社|Mulholland Books}}出版《黑色洛城：剧情碎片》（''L.A. Noire: The Collected Stories''），聘请著名犯罪作家撰写这部短篇小说集，这些故事均基于《黑色洛城》的宇宙<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=34476 |title=News – Rockstar, Mulholland Books Publishing Digital Collection Of L.A. Noire Stories |last=Orland |first=Kyle |website=Gamasutra |date=2011-05-03 |access-date=2011-05-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110508195611/http://www.gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=34476 |archive-date= 2011-05-08 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/15701/announcing-an-original-short-fiction-series-in-honor-of-la-noire.html |title=Announcing an Original Short Fiction Series in Honor of L.A. Noire |publisher=Rockstar Games |date=2011-05-03 |access-date=2011-05-27 |archive-date=2020-10-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201026050613/https://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/15701/announcing-an-original-short-fiction-series-in-honor-of-la-noire.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 员工投诉 ===
{{Main|Team Bondi#争议|l1=Team Bondi争议}}
游戏发行后不久，一群Team Bondi前员工推出网站lanoirecredits.com，收录100多个在游戏的制作人员名单中未出现或写错的名字<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.vg247.com/2011/06/03/l-a-noire-development-staff-offer-corrected-credits/ |title=L.A. Noire development staff offer corrected credits |last=Hiller |first=Brenna |website=VG247 |date=2011-06-03 |access-date=2011-06-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110606080452/http://www.vg247.com/2011/06/03/l-a-noire-development-staff-offer-corrected-credits/ |archive-date=2011-06-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。随后，劳资公司针对游戏开发过程中的工作时长及管理风格提请一系列诉讼和反诉<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gamasutra.com/blogs/DaveHeironymus/20110712/89804/Team_Bondi_My_Side_Of_The_Story.php |title=Team Bondi: My Side of the Story |last=Heironymous |first=David |work=Gamasutra |publisher=UBM plc |date=2011-06-12 |access-date=2014-06-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120509201054/http://www.gamasutra.com/blogs/DaveHeironymus/20110712/89804/Team_Bondi_My_Side_Of_The_Story.php |archive-date=2012-05-09 }}</ref>。一位不具名的开发人员公开讨论了工作室的管理风格、人员流动率、工作时长及其他和《黑色洛城》相关的情况<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ign.com/articles/2011/06/24/why-did-la-noire-take-seven-years-to-make |title=Why Did L.A. Noire Take Seven Years to Make? |last=McMillen |first=Andrew |work=IGN |publisher=Ziff Davis |date=2011-06-24 |access-date=2014-06-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121021232014/http://www.ign.com/articles/2011/06/24/why-did-la-noire-take-seven-years-to-make |archive-date=2012-10-21 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

[[File:LA_Noire_logo.jpg|right]]
2011年7月，工作室员工泄露了一系列的机密电邮，并附上评论<ref name="emails">{{cite web |url=http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2011-07-05-revealed-the-internal-emails-that-provoked-whistle-blowing-at-team-bondi-blog-entry |title=Revealed: The emails behind the whistle blowing at Team Bondi |last=McMillen |first=Andrew |publisher=Gamesindustry.biz |date=2011-07-05 |access-date=2011-07-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110706212311/http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2011-07-05-revealed-the-internal-emails-that-provoked-whistle-blowing-at-team-bondi-blog-entry |archive-date=2011-07-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2011-07-05-la-noire-the-team-bondi-emails-article |title=L.A. Noire: The Team Bondi Emails Article |last=McMillen |first=Andrew |website=Eurogamer |date=2011-07-07 |access-date=2014-06-25 |archive-date=2020-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111162531/https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2011-07-05-la-noire-the-team-bondi-emails-article |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他们称电邮体现Team Bondi和Rockstar的关系存在争议，暗示两家公司不愿再度合作<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.1up.com/news/la-noire-devs-contentious-relationship-rockstar-revealed|title=L.A. Noire Dev's Contentious Relationship with Rockstar Revealed|last=Pereira|first=Chris|date=2011-07-05|website=1UP|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110914174247/http://www.1up.com/news/la-noire-devs-contentious-relationship-rockstar-revealed|archive-date=2011-09-14|access-date=2014-06-25}}</ref>。开发团队的另一名匿名消息人士表示，“很明显，（Rockstar）不会发行Team Bondi的下一部游戏”，“与Rockstar的关系已经被彻底破坏”：

<blockquote>Team Bondi和Rockstar之间的冲突，有部分原因是Rockstar对Team Bondi的方向感到沮丧，Team Bondi的管理层因而对Rockstar包揽众多创意事宜感到不满。同样值得注意的是，Rockstar过去非常想让Team Bondi成为“Rockstar悉尼工作室”之类的东西，他们和Team Bondi的管理层走得越近，就越能感受到这是个糟糕的主意<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2011-07-05-rockstars-disdain-for-la-noire-dev |title=Rockstar's "disdain" for LA Noire dev |last=Yin-Poole |first=Wesley |website=Eurogamer |date=2011-07-05 |access-date=2011-11-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110708182209/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2011-07-05-rockstars-disdain-for-la-noire-dev |archive-date=2011-07-08 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。</blockquote>

Team Bondi最终于2011年8月进入{{le|管理令|Administration (law)}}阶段<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/team-bondi-goes-into-administration/1100-6332196/ |title=Team Bondi goes into administration |last=Parker |first=Laura |work=GameSpot |publisher=CBS Interactive |date=2011-08-31 |access-date=2014-06-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140822135129/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/team-bondi-goes-into-administration/1100-6332196/ |archive-date=2014-08-22 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，同年10月[[清盘|清盘]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2011-10-05-team-bondi-to-be-wound-up-at-creditors-request |title=Team Bondi to be wound up at creditors' request |last=Pearson |first=Dan |publisher=Gamesindustry.biz |date=2011-10-05 |access-date=2014-06-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111006090357/http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2011-10-05-team-bondi-to-be-wound-up-at-creditors-request |archive-date=2011-10-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。公司资产被{{le|肯尼迪·米勒·米切尔|Kennedy Miller Mitchell}}买下<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.kotaku.com.au/2011/08/kmm-in-the-process-of-acquiring-team-bondi-and-its-assets/ |title=KMM In The Process Of Acquiring Team Bondi And Its Assets |last=Serrels |first=Mark |work=Kotaku |publisher=Gawker Media |date=2011-08-10 |access-date=2014-06-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140726213643/http://www.kotaku.com.au/2011/08/kmm-in-the-process-of-acquiring-team-bondi-and-its-assets/ |archive-date=2014-07-26 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，其中包括《[[东方妓女|东方妓女]]》<ref>{{cite web |url=http://kotaku.com/5862886/the-whore-of-the-orient-is-the-next-game-from-la-noires-creator |title=The Whore of the Orient is the Next Game From LA Noire's Creator |last=Plunkett |first=Luke |work=Kotaku |publisher=Gawker Media |date=2011-11-28 |access-date=2014-06-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111130182535/http://kotaku.com/5862886/the-whore-of-the-orient-is-the-next-game-from-la-noires-creator |archive-date=2011-11-30 }}</ref>。Rockstar保留《黑色洛城》的知识产权<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.1up.com/news/la-noire-dev-team-bondi-sells-ip-folding-nearby-studio |title=L.A. Noire Dev Team Bondi Sells IP, Folding Into Nearby Studio |last=Pereira |first=Chris |website=1UP |date=2011-08-09 |access-date=2014-06-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140511153918/http://www.1up.com/news/la-noire-dev-team-bondi-sells-ip-folding-nearby-studio |archive-date=2014-05-11 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。Team Bondi的前员工一部分分流到Rockstar各地的工作室，一部分则归入肯尼迪·米勒·米切尔麾下<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/mad-max-director-buys-rights-to-ex-la-noire-devs-new-project/1100-6346705/ |title=Mad Max director buys rights to ex-L.A. Noire dev's new project |last=Parker |first=Laura |work=GameSpot |publisher=CBS Interactive |date=2011-11-27 |access-date=2014-06-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140220214822/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/mad-max-director-buys-rights-to-ex-la-noire-devs-new-project/1100-6346705/ |archive-date=2014-02-20 }}</ref>。虽然在开发过程中关系陷入僵局，麦克纳马拉对Rockstar还是有正面的评价：“我对Rockstar没有成见，希望这件事情不会让我们感到难过”<ref name="OPM-Mc">{{cite web |url=http://www.officialplaystationmagazine.co.uk/2012/01/25/brendan-mcnamara-interview-creating-la-noire-and-destroying-team-bondi/2/ |title=Brendan McNamara interview: creating LA Noire and destroying Team Bondi |last=Hurley |first=Leon |publisher=Official PlayStation Magazine |date=2012-01-25 |access-date=2014-06-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120127185345/http://www.officialplaystationmagazine.co.uk/2012/01/25/brendan-mcnamara-interview-creating-la-noire-and-destroying-team-bondi/2 |archive-date=2012-01-27 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

