eo |publisher=Rockstar Games |date=2011-03-31 |accessdate=2014-07-24 |archive-date=2014-07-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140728171226/http://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/14911/watch-the-new-la-noire-a-slip-of-the-tongue-traffic-desk-preorde.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。6月21日，改编自{{le|奥康纳电镀厂事故|O'Connor Plating Works Disaster|1947年奥康纳电镀公司爆炸案}}的纵火科案件《尼科尔森电镀厂》（{{lang|en|"Nicholson Electroplating"}}）发布<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/16801/the-real-crimes-behind-la-noire-cases-the-nicholson-electroplati.html |title=The Real Crimes Behind L.A. Noire Cases: "The Nicholson Electroplating Disaster" |publisher=Rockstar Games |date=2011-06-14 |accessdate=2014-07-24 |archive-date=2014-07-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140728205637/http://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/16801/the-real-crimes-behind-la-noire-cases-the-nicholson-electroplati.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。刑事科案件《大麻狂热》（{{lang|en|"Reefer Madness"}}）于2011年7月12日发行，讲述非法[[大麻属|大麻]]销售网络被捣毁的过程<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/17621/la-noire-reefer-madness-dlc-case-now-available-for-download.html |title=L.A. Noire "Reefer Madness" DLC Case Now Available for Download |publisher=Rockstar Games |date=2011-07-12 |accessdate=2014-07-24 |archive-date=2014-07-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140728203611/http://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/17621/la-noire-reefer-madness-dlc-case-now-available-for-download.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。交通科案件《领事的车》（{{lang|en|"The Consul's Car"}}）于2011年7月26日上市，聚焦一起盗车案。该案件原本为PlayStation 3北美版独占内容，后开放欧洲区下载，最终收录于《完整版》<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/18041/la-noire-the-consuls-car-traffic-bonus-case-now-available-for-do.html |title=L.A. Noire "The Consul's Car" Traffic Bonus Case Now Available for Download Worldwide on PlayStation Network |publisher=Rockstar Games |date=2011-07-29 |accessdate=2014-07-24 |archive-date=2014-07-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140728205715/http://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/18041/la-noire-the-consuls-car-traffic-bonus-case-now-available-for-do.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。游戏中的两套西服（Broderick和Sharpshooter）、两把枪（镀镍手枪和[[汤普森冲锋枪|芝加哥钢琴枪]]）和徽章追逐挑战（要求玩家快速搜集游戏世界中的金币）原本为预购内容，之后于2011年5月31日开放下载<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/16561/announcing-la-noire-downloadable-content-details.html |title=Announcing L.A. Noire Downloadable Content Details |publisher=Rockstar Games |date=2011-05-31 |accessdate=2014-07-24 |archive-date=2014-07-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140728204555/http://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/16561/announcing-la-noire-downloadable-content-details.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

