据[[汇总媒体|汇总媒体]][[Metacritic|Metacritic]]，《黑色洛城》获得评论家“普遍好评”<ref name="MCPS3"/><ref name="MC360"/><ref name="MCPC"/>，而在另一個網站[[GameRankings|GameRankings]]，《黑色洛城》的平均分數均在80%以上<ref name="GRPS3" /><ref name="GR360" /><ref name="GRPC" />，其中剧情及面部动画技术普遍获得褒扬<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.industrygamers.com/news/la-noire-currently-tracking-40-behind-red-dead-redemption/ |title=LA Noire Currently Tracking 40% Behind Red Dead Redemption |publisher=IndustryGamers |date=2011-06-15 |accessdate=2011-07-18 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110829060111/http://www.industrygamers.com/news/la-noire-currently-tracking-40-behind-red-dead-redemption |archivedate=2011-08-29 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

首篇评论由英国报纸《[[卫报|卫报]]》发表，文章称赞游戏的配乐完美，有着电影般的质感<ref name="GuardianReview"/>。GameZone将游戏比作[[古典好莱坞电影|古典好莱坞电影]]，指其注重细节，有别于其他游戏<ref name="GameZoneReview"/>。《{{le|PlayStation杂志|PlayStation: The Official Magazine}}》将游戏比作一部精雕细琢、让观众上瘾的[[AMC_(电视频道)|AMC]]电视连续剧<ref name="PTOM"/>。

《[[Edge_(杂志)|Edge]]》称赞了面部技术，但认为尽管游戏的其他主要方面没有其他作品优秀，尽管如此，还是要承认Team Bondi用这样一种时尚、大气且具有凝聚力的方式糅合如此多的游戏类型，是其他开发商无法做到的<ref name="EdgeReview"/>。[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]的卡罗琳·佩蒂（Carolyn Petiti）赞赏游戏的审讯机制及总体风格<ref name="GameSpot Review"/>。《{{le|GamesMaster|GamesMaster (magazine)}}》认为《黑色洛城》是Rockstar最成熟的开放世界游戏<ref>{{cite magazine|date=July 2011|title=L.A. Noire (PS3)|magazine=GamesMaster|page=74}}</ref>。

《[[官方Xbox杂志|官方Xbox杂志]]》称游戏是[[Xbox_360|Xbox 360]]平台最接近《[[暴雨殺機|暴雨殺機]]》的作品，但“漏洞百出”<ref name="OXM"/>。[[IGN|IGN]]认为《黑色洛城》是低配版的《暴雨》，“几乎成功”地为《暴雨》打造了新的架构<ref name="IGN-Review"/>。《[[Joystiq|Joystiq]]》认为《黑色洛城》没像传统意义上一直充满“乐趣”，但“仅仅是有趣”也不让人满意，这使得游戏漏掉了电子游戏玩家平常会留意的某些地方<ref name="JReview"/>。

虽然评价普遍正面，但仍有部分评论人认为有些案件太多余，玩家能控制的地方太少<ref name="IGN-Review"/>，时不时让人觉得无聊<ref name="GI"/>。[[1UP.com|1UP]]给出了完美的分数，但也指出过场动画太长，会让某些玩家觉得失去对动作的控制<ref>{{cite web |last=Atienza |first=Jobert |url=http://www.1up.com/reviews/la-noire-review?pager.offset=0 |title=L.A. Noire Review |website=1UP.com |date=2011-05-16 |accessdate=2011-05-17 |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120204071335/http://www.1up.com/reviews/la-noire-review?pager.offset=0 |archivedate=2012-02-04 }}</ref>。[[GameTrailers|GameTrailers]]总结称，游戏被重复内容给拖累，但与其他游戏相比，对角色本身的要多些，总体体验还不错<ref name="GTR"/>。

虽然使用了动态捕捉技术，游戏角色的身体仍被批评毫无生命力。对此，游戏总监兼编剧布伦丹·麦克纳马拉在接受《Eurogamer》采访时表示，人们对角色面部及身体的评价有着强烈的反差，是因为角色衣服缺少动画。他表示，菲尔普斯对某些线索作出过激反应，是因为游戏原先（给审讯环节）写的剧本是“奉承”、“胁迫”和“谎言”，但游戏出来后改成了“真实、可疑或谎言”，这使得菲尔普斯经常出现玩家能预料到的尴尬反应<ref name="EG2011_11_09"/>。

游戏的VR重制版也获得了较高的评价。The Sixth Axis的吉姆·哈格里夫斯（Jim Hargreaves）认为VR版聪明地回炉了《黑色洛城》这部近十年来最奇妙的游戏作品，Team Bondi一丝不苟、精细的世界建设和技术成就依然在线，可以通过VR版无缝点击，虽然没有什么大的突破<ref>{{cite web |last1=Hargreaves |first1=Jim |title=L.A. Noire: The VR Case Files PSVR Review – TheSixthAxis |url=https://www.thesixthaxis.com/2019/12/12/la-noire-case-files-psvr-review/ |website=The Sixth Axis |accessdate=2021-03-22 |date=2019-12-12 |archive-date=2021-05-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210531120422/https://www.thesixthaxis.com/2019/12/12/la-noire-case-files-psvr-review/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。相比之下，游戏重制版在[[任天堂Switch|任天堂Switch]]掌机表现引来褒贬不一的评价。《CGMagazine》的菲尔·布朗（Phil Brown）认为Rockstar将《黑色洛城》这部被低估的作品移植到Switch平台，实际上给这部老作品加了一些全新的控制手法，没有踟蹰于固有玩法，这点值得赞赏<ref>{{cite web |last1=Brown |first1=Phil |title=L.A. Noire Review (Switch) |url=https://www.cgmagonline.com/reviews/l-a-noire-review-switch/ |website=CGMagazine |accessdate=2021-03-22 |date=2017-11-17 |archive-date=2021-05-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210531122959/https://www.cgmagonline.com/reviews/l-a-noire-review-switch/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。但另一方面，“Nintendo Life”的达米恩·麦克法兰（Damien McFerran）则持保留意见。他认为，早在2011年，《黑色洛城》就不是一部完美无瑕的游戏，而到了重制版，问题依然没有改变。尽管如此，重制版还是超越了当年的风采。我们尊重这款游戏，在接下来的几年把它当成经典的先驱之作。很少游戏作品能像这部游戏那样，用臻至成熟的游戏体验对待玩家，这个态度值得整个游戏行业学习<ref>{{cite web |last1=McFerran |first1=Damien |title=L.A. Noire Review (Switch) |url=https://www.nintendolife.com/reviews/nintendo-switch/l_a_noire |website=Nintendo Life |accessdate=2021-03-22 |date=2017-11-21 |archive-date=2021-05-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210531123039/https://www.nintendolife.com/reviews/nintendo-switch/l_a_noire |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在2012年的英国电影学院游戏大奖上，游戏获得最佳原创配乐奖<ref name="BAFTA"/>，同时获得七项大奖提名<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.gamespot.com/articles/arkham-city-la-noire-lead-bafta-nominations/1100-6350525/ |title=Arkham City, L.A. Noire lead BAFTA nominations |work=GameSpot |date=2012-02-16 |accessdate=2015-06-16 |archive-date=2015-01-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150108042957/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/arkham-city-la-noire-lead-bafta-nominations/1100-6350525/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。而任天堂Switch及VR版则获得IGN的2017年年度奖的最佳重制奖<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ign.com/wikis/best-of-2017-awards/Best_Remake/Remaster |title=Best of 2017 Awards: Best Remake/Remaster |website=IGN |date=2017-12-20 |accessdate=2018-01-28 |archive-date=2018-01-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180108143541/http://www.ign.com/wikis/best-of-2017-awards/Best_Remake/Remaster |dead-url=no }}</ref>，获得2018年纽约游戏奖（New York Game）[[马里奥·库默州长大桥|塔潘齐大桥]]最佳重制奖<ref>{{cite news |last=Ramadge |first=Andrew |url=http://www.news.com.au/technology/gaming/cant-wait-to-go-hunting-for-clues-in-la-noire-youll-have-to-hunt-around-for-a-copy-first/story-e6frfrt9-1226061907016 |title=Can't wait to go hunting for clues in LA Noire? You'll have to hunt around for a copy first |work=Australian Boardcasting Company |date=2011-05-24 |accessdate=2014-06-25 |archive-date=2011-08-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110812060925/http://www.news.com.au/technology/gaming/cant-wait-to-go-hunting-for-clues-in-la-noire-youll-have-to-hunt-around-for-a-copy-first/story-e6frfrt9-1226061907016 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，VR版则获得第16届游戏音频网络工会奖（Game Audio Network Guild Awards）“最佳VR音频”奖<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.audiogang.org/2018-awards/ |title=2018 Awards |publisher=Game Audio Network Guild |accessdate=2018-04-14 |archive-date=2018-04-14 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20180414040621/http://www.audiogang.org/2018-awards/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===销量===
游戏在美国发行当天，Rockstar Games母公司Take-Two Interactive收盘股价上涨7.75％，创下三年来的新高。这次上涨为《黑色洛城》市场表现不俗的反应<ref>{{cite web |last=Citizen |first=Jessica |url=https://www.vg247.com/2011/05/18/l-a-noire-gives-much-needed-boost-to-take-two-shares/ |title=L.A. Noire gives much-needed boost to Take-Two shares |website=VG247 |date=2011-05-18 |accessdate=2011-05-23 |archive-date=2011-05-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110522184523/http://www.vg247.com/2011/05/18/l-a-noire-gives-much-needed-boost-to-take-two-shares/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。根据2012年2月公布的最后一份销量数据，游戏已出货约500万份<ref name="Take2_Q3_2012"/>。

[[NPD集团|NPD集团]]表示，《黑色洛城》是2011年5月美国销量最高的游戏<ref>{{cite web |last=Graft |first=Kris |url=https://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/35201/NPD_May_US_Retail_Game_Industry_Sales_Lowest_Since_Oct_06.php |title=NPD: May U.S. Retail Game Industry Sales Lowest Since Oct. '06 |website=Gamasutra |date=2011-06-13 |accessdate=2011-06-27 |archive-date=2011-06-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110617062130/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/35201/NPD_May_US_Retail_Game_Industry_Sales_Lowest_Since_Oct_06.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>，在PlayStation 3和Xbox 360平台卖出了89.9万份<ref>{{cite web |last=Dutton |first=Fred |url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2011-06-14-la-noire-sales-below-our-estimate |title=LA Noire sales 'below our estimate' |website=Eurogamer |date=2011-06-14 |accessdate=2020-09-23 |archive-date=2018-01-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180129141403/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2011-06-14-la-noire-sales-below-our-estimate |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

游戏登上英国游戏销量榜榜首，成为在该国最为畅销的[[知识产权|新作]]<ref>{{cite web |last=Cullen |first=Johnny |url=https://www.vg247.com/2011/05/23/uk-charts-la-noire-becomes-fastest-selling-new-ip-ever/ |title=UK charts: LA Noire becomes fastest-selling new IP ever |website=VG247 |date=2011-05-23 |accessdate=2011-05-23 |archive-date=2011-05-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110525042903/http://www.vg247.com/2011/05/23/uk-charts-la-noire-becomes-fastest-selling-new-ip-ever/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Sterling |first=Jim |url=https://www.destructoid.com/58-of-l-a-noire-sales-on-xbox-360-42-on-ps3-201813.phtml |title=58% of L.A. Noire sales on Xbox 360, 42% on PS3 |website=Destructoid |date=2011-05-23 |accessdate=2020-09-23 |archive-date=2016-06-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160630133212/https://www.destructoid.com/58-of-l-a-noire-sales-on-xbox-360-42-on-ps3-201813.phtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>，直至被2014年发行的《[[看门狗_(游戏)|看门狗]]》打破<ref>{{cite web |last=Phillips |first=Tom |url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2014-06-02-watch-dogs-is-the-biggest-new-ip-launch-in-the-uk-ever |title=Watch Dogs is the biggest new IP launch in the UK ever |website=Eurogamer |date=2014-06-02 |accessdate=2014-06-25 |archive-date=2014-06-02 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20140602093538/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2014-06-02-watch-dogs-is-the-biggest-new-ip-launch-in-the-uk-ever |dead-url=no }}</ref>。游戏在英国游戏榜维持了三个星期的榜首位置<ref>{{cite web |last=Sliwinski |first=Alexander |url=https://www.engadget.com/2011/06/06/la-noire-guilty-of-being-uk-sales-winner-for-third-week/ |title=LA Noire guilty of being UK sales winner for third week in a row |publisher=Engadget (Joystiq) |date=2011-06-06 |accessdate=2014-06-25 |archive-date=2016-05-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160514032733/http://www.engadget.com/2011/06/06/la-noire-guilty-of-being-uk-sales-winner-for-third-week/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。上市才一个星期，游戏便在澳大利亚主要城市游戏店脱销<ref>{{cite news |last=Ramadge |first=Andrew |url=http://www.news.com.au/technology/gaming/cant-wait-to-go-hunting-for-clues-in-la-noire-youll-have-to-hunt-around-for-a-copy-first/story-e6frfrt9-1226061907016 |title=Can't wait to go hunting for clues in LA Noire? You'll have to hunt around for a copy first |work=Australian Broadcasting Comapny |date=2011-05-24 |accessdate=2014-06-25 |archive-date=2011-08-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110812060925/http://www.news.com.au/technology/gaming/cant-wait-to-go-hunting-for-clues-in-la-noire-youll-have-to-hunt-around-for-a-copy-first/story-e6frfrt9-1226061907016 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。7月7日，游戏在日本发行，PlayStation 3和Xbox 360平台销量共71057份。其中PlayStation 3版凭借58,436份销量位列榜首，Xbox 360版占12,621份销量<ref>{{cite web |last=Nunneley |first=Stephany |url=https://www.vg247.com/2011/07/13/japanese-charts-%E2%80%93-l-a-noire-debuts-psp-hits-the-top-once-more/ |title=Japanese charts – L.A. Noire debuts, PSP hits the top once more |website=VG247 |date=2011-07-13 |accessdate=2020-09-23 |archive-date=2018-03-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180311150400/https://www.vg247.com/2011/07/13/japanese-charts-%e2%80%93-l-a-noire-debuts-psp-hits-the-top-once-more/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author=Ishaan |url=http://www.siliconera.com/2011/07/13/this-week-in-sales-l-a-noire-takes-the-lead/ |title=This Week In Sales: L.A. Noire Takes The Lead |publisher=Siliconera |date=2011-07-13 |accessdate=2011-07-13 |archive-date=2011-07-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110719073318/http://www.siliconera.com/2011/07/13/this-week-in-sales-l-a-noire-takes-the-lead/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==疑似续集==
2011年5月22日，麦克纳马拉表示，在现有的技术条件下，《黑色洛城》续集的开发时间会比第一部缩短五年<ref>{{cite web |first=John |last=Gaudiosi |url=http://www.gamerlive.tv/article/brendan-mcnamara-explains-why-la-noire-2-won%E2%80%99t-take-long-make |title=Brendan McNamara Explains Why LA Noire 2 Won’t Take as Long to Make |publisher=GamerLive.TV |date=2011-05-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120423060617/http://www.gamerlive.tv/article/brendan-mcnamara-explains-why-la-noire-2-won%E2%80%99t-take-long-make |archive-date=2012-04-23 |dead-url=yes |accessdate=2011-05-24 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Cullen |first=Johnny |url=http://www.vg247.com/2011/05/23/mcnamara-la-noire-sequel-wont-take-five-years-to-make/ |title=McNamara: Future Team Bondi projects won’t take five years to make |website=VG247 |date=2011-05-23 |accessdate=2014-06-25 |archive-date=2014-05-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140530074749/http://www.vg247.com/2011/05/23/mcnamara-la-noire-sequel-wont-take-five-years-to-make/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在同一个礼拜举行的投资者电话会议上，Take-Two Interactive首席执行官施特劳斯·泽尼克（Strauss Zelnick）表示《黑色洛城》是“非常成功的作品”，他们有“充分理由认为《黑色洛城》会是本公司又一个强大的品牌”，重申他们“的确将《黑色洛城》看作成强有力的品牌”<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/34816/TakeTwo_LA_Noire_First_Week_Very_Successful.php |title=News – Take-Two: L.A. Noire First Week 'Very Successful' |website=Gamasutra |accessdate=2011-05-25 |archive-date=2011-05-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110528042459/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/34816/TakeTwo_LA_Noire_First_Week_Very_Successful.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2011年11月的另一场投资者电话会议中，泽尼克重申《黑色洛城》对Take-Two的重要性，指游戏“已成为公司重要的品牌”。他说，游戏是Take-Two上一个财年中“最成功的新作”，已成为其投资组合中的关键资产<ref>{{cite web |last=Dutton |first=Fred |url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2011-11-08-take-two-la-noire-has-become-an-important-franchise |title=Take-Two: LA Noire "has become an important franchise" |publisher=Eurogamer.net |date=2011-05-20 |accessdate=2011-11-09 |archive-date=2011-11-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111110224941/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2011-11-08-take-two-la-noire-has-become-an-important-franchise |dead-url=no }}</ref>。同月，麦克纳马拉宣布下一部游戏名叫《[[东方妓女|东方妓女]]》，讲述了“20世纪一个不为人知的伟大故事”。该项目由KMM互动娱乐（KMM Interactive Entertainment）开发，该工作室由肯尼迪·米勒·米切尔于2011年8月收购Team Bondi大部分资产成立<ref>{{cite web |url=http://kotaku.com/5862886/the-whore-of-the-orient-is-the-next-game-from-la-noires-creator |title=The Whore of the Orient is the Next Game From LA Noire’s Creator |website=Kotaku |first=Luke |last=Plunkett |date=2011-11-28 |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111130182535/http://kotaku.com/5862886/the-whore-of-the-orient-is-the-next-game-from-la-noires-creator |archivedate=2011-11-30 |accessdate=2020-09-22 }}</ref>。游戏最终于2016年6月宣布取消<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.pcgamer.com/whore-of-the-orient-the-spiritual-successor-to-la-noire-isnt-going-to-happen/ |title=Whore of the Orient, the spiritual successor to LA Noire, isn't going to happen |last=Chalk |first=Andy |work=PC Gamer |date=2016-06-25 |accessdate=2016-06-27 |archive-date=2016-06-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160627061155/http://www.pcgamer.com/whore-of-the-orient-the-spiritual-successor-to-la-noire-isnt-going-to-happen/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2012年2月13日，Rockstar Games回答粉丝提问，其中一个问题关于《黑色洛城》品牌的未来发展趋向。Rockstar表示“正考虑在未来将《黑色洛城》打造成一个系列”，但“不急于制作续集”。他们也表示目前的版本不会有追加下载内容或附加内容开发<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/20351/asked-answered-max-payne-3-and-more.html |title=Asked & Answered: Max Payne 3 and More... |publisher=Rockstar Games |date=2012-02-13 |accessdate=2012-05-23 |archive-date=2012-05-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120502022125/http://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/20351/asked-answered-max-payne-3-and-more.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2013年3月，Take-Two Interactive首席运营官卡尔·斯拉托夫（Karl Slatoff）表示公司有“大量未公布的作品正在开发中”，指《黑色洛城》品牌对公司很重要<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/take-two-has-extensive-pipeline-of-unannounced-titles-in-development/1100-6404968/ |title=Take-Two has 'extensive pipeline' of unannounced titles in development |website=GameSpot |last=Makuch |first=Eddie |date=2013-03-07 |accessdate=2013-04-07 |archive-date=2013-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131109085419/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/take-two-has-extensive-pipeline-of-unannounced-titles-in-development/1100-6404968/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

